Comments: TPC Scottsdale isn't the only great stadium golf course for spectators. A few others are coming up on the PGA Tour schedule.

The Cypress Point Club in Pebble Beach, California has incredible ocean views. The Wade Hampton Golf Club in Cashiers, North Carolina is breathtaking in the fall. The Masters are often held at the courses in Pebble Beach, California and Augusta, Georgia. If you're a golf enthusiast, these are a must see.
